                    Via Nicola Dorati 44, Localit√† Granaiola, Bagni di Lucca (LU), Italy.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[#d9b130]">
                    2. Use of the Site
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Users agree to use the Site in accordance with the law, these Terms of Service,
                    and principles of good faith and fairness. Any use of the Site that may:
