                    of the new terms.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[#d9b130]">
                    9. Governing Law and Jurisdiction
                </h2>
                <p>
                    These Terms of Service are governed by Italian law. For any dispute arising from
                    the interpretation or execution of these terms, the Court of Lucca shall have
                    exclusive jurisdiction.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[#d9b130]">
